window.bookSummaryJSON = "Acclaimed author Michael Robotham conquered international best-seller lists with this electrifying thriller. <p> After a woman is brutally slain, investigators bring psychiatrist Joe O'Loughlin in for expert consultation. Joe is shocked to discover the dead woman is a former patient of his who cried rape when he rebuffed her sexual advances. Citing doctor/patient confidentiality, Joe hides this information. But the truth emerges, and suddenly he is the prime suspect.</p>"; 
